---
// Cost estimator — pages/day × words × model rate.
---

<section id="pricing">
  <p class="eyebrow">
    <span class="num">09</span><span data-i18n="price.eye"
      >Bring your own cost</span
    >
  </p>
  <h2 class="serif">
    <span data-i18n="price.t1">Margin is free.</span>
    <em data-i18n="price.t2">Your API bill</em><span data-i18n="price.t3"
      > is yours.</span
    >
  </h2>
  <p class="section-lede" data-i18n="price.lede">
    There is no Margin subscription. The only cost is the provider's per-token
    rate, paid directly to OpenAI, Anthropic, or Google. Most reading sessions
    are measured in cents.
  </p>

  <div class="pricing-grid">
    <div class="calc">
      <h4 data-i18n="price.calc">Cost estimator · monthly</h4>

      <div class="calc-row">
        <span data-i18n="price.pages">Pages translated / day</span>
        <span class="v" id="calcPagesV">10</span>
      </div>
      <input type="range" id="calcPages" min="1" max="100" value="10" step="1" />

      <div class="calc-row">
        <span data-i18n="price.words">Avg. words / page</span>
        <span class="v" id="calcWordsV">1,200</span>
      </div>
      <input
        type="range"
        id="calcWords"
        min="200"
        max="5000"
        value="1200"
        step="100"
      />

      <div class="calc-row" style="margin-bottom:10px">
        <span data-i18n="price.model">Model</span>
        <span class="v" id="calcModelV">GPT-4o mini</span>
      </div>
      <div class="pick" id="calcModelPick">
        <button data-rate="0.15" class="on" type="button">GPT-4o mini</button>
        <button data-rate="2.50" type="button">GPT-4o</button>
        <button data-rate="0.80" type="button">Haiku 3.5</button>
        <button data-rate="3.00" type="button">Sonnet 3.7</button>
        <button data-rate="0.10" type="button">Gemini Flash</button>
      </div>

      <div class="calc-out">
        <div>
          <div class="v"><em>$</em><span id="calcDay">0.07</span></div>
          <div class="l" data-i18n="price.per_day">per day</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="v"><em>$</em><span id="calcMonth">2.16</span></div>
          <div class="l" data-i18n="price.per_month">per month</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <ul class="price-notes">
      <li>
        <div class="n">$.01</div>
        <div data-i18n="price.n1">
          A typical research paper (≈10k words) translated end-to-end with
          GPT-4o mini comes in under one cent.
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="n">$.00</div>
        <div data-i18n="price.n2">
          Cached pages cost zero. Margin's persistent cache means re-reading a
          translated page never re-bills you.
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="n">B Y O</div>
        <div data-i18n="price.n3">
          Bring your own key. The endpoint is editable — plug in any
          compatible gateway, self-hosted router, or routed proxy.
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="n">FREE</div>
        <div data-i18n="price.n4">
          Gemini's free tier is generous enough for casual reading. Most users
          never see a bill at all.
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
